sentences: On the agenda (FCCC/SBSTA/2013/4), SBSTA Chair Richard Muyungi (Tanzania) proposed including a new sub-item on clarification of the text in section G, Article 3.7 ter of the Doha Amendment under the item on methodological issues under the Protocol.
Parties agreed, adopting the agenda and agreeing to the organization of work.
On opening statements, the SBSTA also agreed that parties submit these to the Secretariat for posting online.
